Camoflage::

She kept  her paws over her optics. But her ears perked up when he 
mentioned toys. "Toys? You like toys too? Do you have a 
CyberBattleStation 2 at your place?  I can play Battlepods. It's 
really fun to fight and blast with those. I played Uncle Gearshift 
for a whole week one hot season. He was really good at it. I wasn't 
so good. But I always beat Daddy at it. Wanna play Battlepods if you 
have a BattleStation? Huh? Can we?" she said, still holding her paws 
to her face.
